title Fluxo Completo do Pipeline â€” Etapas 1, 2 e 3\n(GithubMiner + AdjacencyListGraph + GraphAnalytics)

actor       "UsuĂ¡rio"          as User
participant "main.py"          as Main
participant "GithubMiner\n(Etapa 1)" as Miner
